SIMPLE: unvalued
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unvalued
<hw>Un*val"ued</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
valued; not appraised; hence, not considered; disregarded; valueless;
<as>as, an <ex>unvalued</ex> estate</as>.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Unvalued</xex> persons.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having inestimable value; invaluable.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The golden apples of <qex>unvalued</qex> price.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unvariable</ent>⟦br⟧
